spec_data.Name: golang-googlecode-goprotobuf-devel
spec_data.Description:
This package provides  a library that implements run-time support for
encoding (marshaling), decoding (unmarshaling), and accessing protocol
buffers in the Go language.

Install golang-googlecode-goprotobuf for the related protocol compiler plugin.

This package contains library source intended for
building other packages which use import path with
github.com/golang/protobuf prefix.
